+# Slice 007R: Legacy Approval History and Frozen Identity Closure
+
+## Status
+Not Started
+
+## Parent Epic
+Epic 007: Sanction Approval Workflow and Registers
+Epic file: `docs/epics/007-sanction-approval-workflow.md`
