+  public boundaries; it must not repeat a direct `DocumentFile` query, trust download permission as
+  reference authority, or guess that `fpc`/`producer_institution` maps to source `FPO`.
+- Add a regression proving an application cannot generate from a template/file row that predates or
+  bypasses the 008A2 boundary, even when the actor holds template manage and file download
+  permissions. The denial leaves no generated bytes, metadata, audit, or workflow evidence.
+
 ## Visual Acceptance Criteria
 None.
 
